  "title": "1 Year Call Centre Officer - Sembawang (Up to $2,000)  #NJN",
  "description": "<p><strong>Working Hours:</strong></p><p>8.30am – 5.30pm (Mon-Fri)</p><p>8.30am – 12.30pm (Alternate Sat) </p><p><strong>Location:</strong> Senoko Avenue (Pickup available from <strong>Sembawang MRT</strong> upon commencement of work)</p><p><u><strong>Job Description</strong></u></p><ul><li>Contact customer to arrange for appointments for the installation or cut-off of gas pipes / gas water heater or appliances.</li><li>Handle customers’ enquiries on appointments, installation charges and other gas installation related matter.</li><li>Follow up on customer’s enquiries from emails.</li><li>Send SMS/emails to customers on their appointment schedules.</li><li>Promote gas appliances / collaborations with other business partners to potential customers.</li><li>Liaise with term contractor/SP Services on any services lapse.</li><li>Feedback on any difficult/special cases.</li><li>Any other duties as assigned by supervisor</li></ul><p><br />Jessica Nguyen Huynh Thanh Truc<br />CEI Reg. No. R23113787<br />EA License No. 99C4599<br />We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p><p></p>",
